dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents paths worn by the passage of people or animals (trails and tracks)  Cuba. Data for Global Map Cuba were transformed from Digital Topographical Map 1:250 000 of Cuba provided by GEOCUBA, Cuba.Global Map data were developed under the cooperation of National Geospatial Information Authorities (NGIAs) of respective countries and regions.
